{
  "stem": "15768.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And of course, my mother was absolutely convinced that I was not going to come back.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I believe the farmer's wife also felt that this was not a very good situation.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "At any rate, with the soldiers who were quite civil-- and I had made up my mind as I got into this very tight spot-- that they were young soldiers.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I was going to talk to them the way I would have talked to my cousin and hang loose, limit my German to the necessary things, and do most of it in French, fluent French.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As we went around the countryside, of course, the first thing they asked is how come I spoke German out of all these people there?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said that I-- I had a German grandmother who used to speak to me in German.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that is why I knew the language.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so we went from farm to farm all day long and questioned about the pigeons, searched the loft.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And of course, now as an adult, as I look back, I'm absolutely certain that had there been carrier pigeons, the French farmers would have hid them anyway and not had them in their loft available for Germans to pick up.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But it-- it seemed like a fairly serious task.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were gone all day.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was dark when they were finally decided to end the day.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They bought me a very long French bread as a reward for my efforts and brought-- brought me back to the farm, and where everybody stood in disbelief, my mother, of course, her face tear-stained and-- and super-apprehensive, and my father as well.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But there I was, shipshape and back.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
